ric/screenshots\" target=\"_blank\">\n    <img width=\"98%\" src=\"https://gitlab.com/billyg270/conveyor-belts/-/raw/master/readme_assets/preview_images.png\" alt=\"Discord\" data-testid=\"image\" />\n</a>\n\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\n<h2>Crafting</h2>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n    <img width=\"33%\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 10px solid black; border-radius:40px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-right: 5px;\" src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/903385978482360320/958339548885164053/unknown.png\" alt=\"Wood belt\" data-testid=\"image\"/><img width=\"32%\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 10px solid black; border-radius:40px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-right: 5px;\" src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/903385978482360320/958339626987294770/unknown.png\" alt=\"Iron belt\" data-testid=\"image\"/><img width=\"33%\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 10px solid black; border-radius:40px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-right: 5px;\" src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/903385978482360320/958339652950065172/unknown.png\" alt=\"Gold belt\" data-testid=\"image\"/>\n    <br />\n    <img width=\"33%\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 10px solid black; border-radius:40px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-right: 5px;\" src=\"https://gitlab.com/billyg270/conveyor-belts/-/raw/master/readme_assets/wood_belt_uses.png\" alt=\"Filter and upward slope\" data-testid=\"image\"/>\n    <br />\n    <img width=\"33%\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 10px solid black; border-radius:40px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-right: 5px;\" src=\"https://gitlab.com/billyg270/conveyor-belts/-/raw/master/readme_assets/upward_wood_belt_uses.png\" alt=\"Downward slope\" data-testid=\"image\"/><img width=\"33%\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 10px solid black; border-radius:40px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-right: 5px;\" src=\"https://gitlab.com/billyg270/conveyor-belts/-/raw/master/readme_assets/downward_wood_belt_uses.png\" alt=\"Slope to regular\" data-testid=\"image\"/>\n</div>\n\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\n<h2>Videos</h2>\n\n<ul style=\"text-decoration: none;\">\n    <li>\n        <a href=\"https://youtu.be/txjlByWaO9A\">Redstone: Belts can be disabled with a redstone input</a>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <a href=\"https://youtu.be/WlYpflEd5pQ\">Filtering: With no filters set, items will be split evenly between the two outputs</a>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <a href=\"https://youtu.be/p8wqFzgI7Zo\">Filtering: With a filter set on one side, that item will go to that output and all other items will go to the other one</a>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <a href=\"https://youtu.be/HToJ1V1V7DU\">Filtering: With both filters set, items will go to the output with the filter on, if the item matches neither filter a sound will be played to indicate it is jammed</a>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <a href=\"https://youtu.be/P-Aj1fbJZYc\">Merging: Items will 'zipper merge' when going onto a belt, either from hoppers or other belts</a>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n        <a href=\"https://youtu.be/oxQ9kWJKpd4\">Placement: Belts will face away from you when placed. Holding shift will make them face towards you</a>\n    </li>\n</ul>",
